contentrichtext.text: {{Taxobox | image = | status = EX | status_system = IUCN2.3 | regnum = [[Animalia]] | phylum = [[Mollusca]] | classis = [[Gastropoda]] | unranked_superfamilia = clade [[Heterobranchia]] clade [[Euthyneura]]<br/>clade [[Panpulmonata]]<br/> clade [[Eupulmonata]]<br/> clade [[Stylommatophora]]<br/> clade [[Sigmurethra]]<br/> clade [[limacoid clade]] | superfamilia = [[Helicarionoidea]] | familia = [[Helicarionidae]] | genus = ''[[Quintalia]]'' | species = '''''Q. stoddartii''''' | binomial = ''Quintalia stoddartii'' | binomial_authority = [[John Edward Gray|Gray]], 1834 | synonyms = }} '''''Quintalia stoddartii''''' is an [[extinct]] [[species]] of air-breathing [[land snail]] or [[semislug]], a [[Terrestrial animal|terrestrial]] [[pulmonate]] [[gastropod]] [[mollusk]] in the family [[Helicarionidae]]. This species was [[Endemism|endemic]] to [[Norfolk Island]]. ==References== {{reflist}} * Mollusc Specialist Group 1996.
